CODE:
 public class S123 {
        public static void main(String[] args) {
            Scanner obj=new Scanner(System.in);
            String a=obj.next();
            String org=a;
            int b=a.length();
            String e= "";
            for(int i=b-1;i>=0;--i){
                e+=a.charAt(i);
            }
            System.out.println(e);
            if(org.equals(e)){
                System.out.println("palindrome");
            }
            else{
                System.out.println("Not a palindrome");
            }

        }


    }
OUTPUT:
noon
noon
palindrome


satya
aytas
Not a palindrome
